{"ikmk_mds_id":"18220596","ikmk_id":"21680","eLearning_completed":"0","primary_source_id":"0","title":"Preu\u00dfen: Friedrich Wilhelm III.","inventory_number":"","activated":"yes","item":{"ikmk_item_id":"1","ndp_uri":"https:\/\/ikmk.smb.museum\/ndp\/item\/1","item_de":"M\u00fcnze","item_en":"Coin","item_nomisma":"http:\/\/nomisma.org\/id\/coin"},"permalink":"https:\/\/ikmk.smb.museum\/object?id=18220596","permalink_source":null,"publisher":{"ikmk_publisher_id":13,"ndp_uri":"https:\/\/ikmk.smb.museum\/ndp\/owner\/13","publisher_name":"M\u00fcnzkabinett, Staatliche Museen zu Berlin - Stiftung Preu\u00dfischer Kulturbesitz","publisher_isil":"http:\/\/ld.zdb-services.de\/resource\/organisations\/DE-MUS-814819","publisher_isil_short":"DE-MUS-814819","UID":"http:\/\/ld.zdb-services.de\/resource\/organisations\/DE-MUS-814819\/18220596","legalBodyWeblink":"https:\/\/www.smb.museum\/museen-und-einrichtungen\/muenzkabinett\/home.html","nomisma_address":"http:\/\/nomisma.org\/id\/mk_berlin","author":"Bannicke, Elke"},"owner":{"ikmk_owner_id":"13","owner_name":"Berlin, M\u00fcnzkabinett der Staatlichen Museen","owner_isil":"http:\/\/ld.zdb-services.de\/resource\/organisations\/DE-MUS-814819","owner_isil_short":"DE-MUS-814819","owner_www_address":"https:\/\/ikmk.smb.museum\/","nomisma_address":"http:\/\/nomisma.org\/id\/mk_berlin","ndp_uri":"https:\/\/ikmk.smb.museum\/ndp\/owner\/13","owner_type":{"de":"Eigentum","en":"Property","ikmk_type_id":"2","ndp_uri":"https:\/\/ikmk.smb.museum\/ndp\/status_of_property\/2"}},"ikmk_status_id":"7","status":{"de":"vorhanden","en":"present","ikmk_status_id":"7","ndp_uri":"https:\/\/ikmk.smb.museum\/ndp\/object_status\/7"},"nominal":{"ikmk_nominal_id":"1909","nominal_de":"Taler (Vereinstaler)","nominal_en":"Taler (Vereinstaler)","nominal_nomisma_id":"http:\/\/nomisma.org\/id\/taler_(vereinstaler)","nominal_gnd_id":"","info_de":"Auf Grundlage entweder des M\u00fcnzvertrags von Dresden 1838 oder jenes von Wien aus dem Jahr 1857 gepr\u00e4gte Taler und Doppeltaler werden auch als Vereinstaler- bzw. Vereinsdoppeltaler bezeichnet.\r\nDer 1838 zwischen den Staaten des Deutschen Zollvereins geschlossene M\u00fcnzvertrag machte den 14- Talerfuss (24 1\/2-Gulden) gerechnet auf die Feine K\u00f6lner Mark zu 233,85 Gramm verbindlich.\r\nDer 1857 zwischen den Staaten des Deutschen M\u00fcnzvereins und \u00d6sterreich schrieb diesen Fu\u00df, nun gerechnet auf 30 Taler aus dem Zollpfund zu 500 Gramm, fort. Die letzten Vereinstaler wurden in \u00d6sterreich 1866 und in Deutschland 1872 gepr\u00e4gt.\r\n\r\nLit.: F. von Schr\u00f6tter, W\u00f6rterbuch der M\u00fcnzkunde (1930) s.v. Vereinstaler 718 (zum Vertrag von 1857).","info_en":"Talers and double talers which are based on the coin treaty of Dresden of 1838 and the one signed in Vienna in 1857 are also called Vereinstaler resp. Vereinsdoppeltaler.\r\nThey are based on the 14 Taler standard based on the Colongne Mark of 233.85 grams.\r\nThe 1857 agreement uses the same standard, now calculated on the Zollpfund of 500 grams, from which 30 Talers are struck.\r\nThe last Vereinstalers were issued in Austria in 1866 and in Germany in 1872.\r\n\r\nLit.: F. von Schr\u00f6tter, W\u00f6rterbuch der M\u00fcnzkunde (1930) s.v. Vereinstaler p. 718 (on the 1857 agreement).","ndp_uri":"https:\/\/ikmk.smb.museum\/ndp\/denomination\/1909"},"date_last":"2023-03-14 01:49:51","coin_status":[{"ikmk_coin_status_id":"36","coin_status_name_de":"K\u00f6nigtum (MA\/NZ)","coin_status_name_en":"Kingdom (medieval\/modern)","coin_status_nomisma_id":"http:\/\/nomisma.org\/id\/king","ndp_uri":"https:\/\/ikmk.smb.museum\/ndp\/class_status\/36"}],"mint":[{"ikmk_country_id":"19","country_ndp_url":"https:\/\/ikmk.smb.museum\/ndp\/country\/19","country_name_de":"Deutschland","country_name_en":"Germany","country_nomisma_id":"http:\/\/nomisma.org\/id\/bundesrepublik_deutschland","country_geoname_id":"http:\/\/www.geonames.org\/2921044","ikmk_region_id":"58","region_ndp_uri":"https:\/\/ikmk.smb.museum\/